    "88551086": {
      "title": "Tropane alkaloids from Lycium barbarum Linn. in vivo and in vitro",
      "abstract": "Tropane alkaloids, which are pharmacologically important compounds, have been reported from solanaceous plants such as Atropa, Hyoscyamus, Datura, Duboisia and Scopolia. However, there is no report on the production of tropane alkaloids from intact plant parts and in tissue culture of Lycium barbarum of an Indian arid zone. Therefore the present investigation was undertaken"
    }
